00:00:41.000 --> 00:00:45.049
It will be done as you can see.

00:00:46.000 --> 00:00:48.321
If you cut it narrowly, it gets fine.

00:00:49.000 --> 00:00:52.180
And if you cut it widely, it gets bold.

00:00:53.000 --> 00:01:00.045
What the point is cut it in small because if you cut it widely, it tears easily.

00:01:04.000 --> 00:01:10.383
I wanted designs near the waist, so I cut it when I was wearing the tight.

00:01:11.000 --> 00:01:16.640
The tights will get impact because I wore a mustard color under green color tight.

00:01:17.000 --> 00:01:18.917
And then, let's make a top.

00:01:19.400 --> 00:01:24.840
Cut the inside leg and make a hole for a head.

00:01:26.000 --> 00:01:32.030
Cut parts of ankles for arms, it fits me very well like a bodysuit.

00:01:34.000 --> 00:01:38.122
Wear a mustard color tight after cut it in the same way.

00:01:40.000 --> 00:01:42.222
Next, I wanna make a design for the arms.

00:01:43.000 --> 00:01:47.436
Cut the inner thighs in the same way as the first.

00:01:48.000 --> 00:01:52.120
You should cut it as you did before.

00:01:53.000 --> 00:01:55.149
It will be done just like before.

00:01:56.000 --> 00:01:58.485
And then, I wanna knit it.

00:01:59.000 --> 00:02:01.353
How to knit is very easy.

00:02:02.000 --> 00:02:04.818
1,Take the second string is under the first one.

00:02:06.000 --> 00:02:08.069
2.The third one is under the next one.

00:02:09.000 --> 00:02:12.287
Repeat knitting it.

00:02:15.000 --> 00:02:19.497
