00:02:53.000 --> 00:02:56.520
Next, let's make TMNT turtle shell costume!

00:02:57.000 --> 00:03:01.660
At first, what you need are a bamboo basket, newspaper and a packing tape.

00:03:01.820 --> 00:03:05.320
If you don't have a bamboo basket, don't worry. 

00:03:05.320 --> 00:03:08.320
At least you need a newspaper and a packing tape.

00:03:09.000 --> 00:03:13.520
Crumple newspapers into a ball as you can see and put it on the bamboo basket.

00:03:14.000 --> 00:03:19.160
Then, tape it with a packing tape.

00:03:19.380 --> 00:03:22.200
Fix it like a carapace.

00:03:22.480 --> 00:03:28.520
If you wanna make a real carapace, make the top part  bigger.

00:03:28.880 --> 00:03:32.500
Make it like a half size of avocado. 

00:03:33.000 --> 00:03:37.546
Wrap it with a packaging tape to cover newspapers.

00:03:39.000 --> 00:03:43.179
Add some newspaper if you need more bulge.

00:03:45.000 --> 00:03:49.436
Add some newspaper to the inside and cover it in the same way.

00:03:50.000 --> 00:03:54.000
I recommend you to use not a paper packing tape, but a cloth packing tape.

00:03:54.000 --> 00:03:57.280
And then, put two strings to carry it on my back.

00:03:58.000 --> 00:04:04.129
It doesn't necessary to use the same string as me.

00:04:04.900 --> 00:04:06.560
The last thing to do is paint.

00:04:07.000 --> 00:04:14.940
I use oily markers which color are brown, ocher, green and black.

00:04:16.000 --> 00:04:19.000
First of all, Draw a design of carapace with brown color.

00:04:19.000 --> 00:04:23.661
Next, color the edge of the designs in deep with ocher.

00:04:23.661 --> 00:04:26.000
and color the inside of the designs in light and blend them.

00:04:26.000 --> 00:04:30.288
You should blend them quickly if you use a oily marker.

00:04:31.000 --> 00:04:35.897
I recommend you to blend them soon after you draw the design and repeat it.

00:04:37.000 --> 00:04:41.133
Then, Color them with brown in the same way.

00:04:42.000 --> 00:04:47.400
It looks like a real carapace because of the texture of the packing tape and newspapers.

00:04:48.000 --> 00:04:52.000
To show color in deep, add black color and green color.

00:04:52.000 --> 00:04:57.000
Follow the design with black color to emphasize and add green on the black color.

00:04:57.000 --> 00:05:01.975
Back the brown color and repeat drawing.

